                <li>Rexam Chief Executive Officer Safety Award for achieving one million hours with zero lost time incidents in 2011.</li>
                <li>Total Incident Rate has reduced steadily from 11.19 in 2009, to 3.49 in 2013.</li>
                <li>Evacuation drill time improved by 71% in response time, between 2011 and 2013. Guatemala is part of the “Ring of Fire,” an area where a large number of earthquakes and volcanic eruptions occur in the basin of the Pacific Ocean.</li>
                <li>Promoted the “Infinitely Recyclable” message of the aluminum can in Guatemala with billboards and educational programs.</li>
