                <li>Eight certified Green Belts (Quality Process analyst, Predictive Maintenance technician, Front End responsible, Back End responsible, Customer Service, General Accounting, Chemical Area coordinator and Raw Material analyst).</li>
                <li>92 Yellow Belts (Quality, Engineering, Production, Finance, Sales and Logistics, IT and Human Resources areas).</li>
                <li>Number of customer complaints per billion produced has reduced steadily from 112.07 in 2007, to 4.57 in 2014, for a reduction of 96% over those years.</li>
                <li>Coca-Cola, InBev, SAB Miller, Heineken and Pepsi Certified.</li>
