        <h5>Employee Morale</h5>
        <p>
          <ul class="square">
                <li>Absenteeism has remained at low levels during the last seven years.</li>
                <li>Turnover was reduced from 2.23% in 2008 to 0.80% in 2014.</li>
                <li>95% of the people are extremely satisfied with ECA as a place to work and 97% of the people are proud to work for ECA.</li>
                <li>We offer English speaking classes because the technology of can making is English language based. This is an advantage for technical learning.</li>
                <li>Nine (9) Health Fairs are offered annually with an in-plant medical doctor.</li>
